OL,3,CWoman settles case over alleged sexual
OL,4,Charassment at a work Christmas dinner
OL,6,FA woman has settled a case of alleged
OL,7,Fsexual harassment at a work Christmas
OL,8,Fdinner.
OL,10,FFernanda Hermosilla settled her case
OL,11,Fagainst a colleague for #21,000 and
OL,12,Fagainst her employer, the Northern
OL,13,FIreland Human Rights Commission, for
OL,14,F#15,000.
OL,16,FMs Hermosilla, who was supported by
OL,17,Fthe Equality Commission for Northern
OL,18,FIreland, attended a staff Christmas
OL,19,Fdinner in December 2022.
