OL,3,CWoman settles case over alleged sexual
OL,4,Charassment at a work Christmas dinner
OL,6,FShe said, during the evening, she
OL,7,Fexperienced unwanted and inappropriate
OL,8,Fphysical contact by a colleague, which
OL,9,Fwas witnessed by other colleagues.
OL,11,FWhen she returned to work on Monday
OL,12,Fmorning, she was informed by her
OL,13,Femployer that an investigation into
OL,14,Fevents during that evening was being
OL,15,Fconducted after the colleague who had
OL,16,Fwitnessed the incident made a formal
OL,17,Fcomplaint.
