OL,6,FDuring the investigation, Ms
OL,7,FHermosilla said she advised her
OL,8,Femployer of an earlier incident of
OL,9,Finappropriate touching, at a non-work
OL,10,Fevent, that she said happened a few
OL,11,Fweeks before with the same colleague
OL,12,Fat a Belfast nightclub.
OL,14,FMs Hermosilla said she had been very
OL,15,Fupset following that incident but had
OL,16,Fbeen reluctant to make a complaint
OL,17,Fbecause she was new to her role.
