OL,6,FWhile the internal investigation was
OL,7,Funderway, Ms Hermosilla worked from
OL,8,Fthe office and the colleague worked
OL,9,Ffrom home.
OL,11,FHowever, she claims that despite this
OL,12,Fshe still worked remotely with this
OL,13,Fcolleague, which she found very
OL,14,Fdifficult.
OL,16,FFollowing the investigation, Ms
OL,17,FHermosilla said she believes her
OL,18,Femployer did not communicate clearly
OL,19,Fwith her about either the outcome of
OL,20,Fthe investigation or the disciplinary
OL,21,Faction taken.
