OL,3,CWoman settles case over alleged sexual
OL,4,Charassment at a work Christmas dinner
OL,6,FMs Hermosilla described "a very
OL,7,Fdifficult time" but said she was glad
OL,8,Fshe "took a stand".
OL,10,F"I did not want or ask for any of
OL,11,Fthis. I was excited to move to Belfast
OL,12,Fto start a new job and advance my
OL,13,Fcareer. This has been a very stressful
OL,14,Fexperience," she said.
OL,16,F"But I'm glad that I took a stand.
OL,17,FEveryone must know what unacceptable
OL,18,Fbehaviour is and what I experienced
OL,19,Fwas wrong.
