OL,3,CWoman settles case over alleged sexual
OL,4,Charassment at a work Christmas dinner
OL,6,F"I want other women to know that they
OL,7,Fdon't have to accept this type of
OL,8,Fbehaviour in the office or at work
OL,9,Fparties and that they should always
OL,10,Fexpect to be supported appropriately
OL,11,Fby their employer.
OL,13,F"I'm glad my case is resolved and now
OL,14,FI want to put this behind me and move
OL,15,Fon with my life."
OL,17,FGeraldine McGahey, chief commissioner,
OL,18,FEquality Commission for Northern
OL,19,FIreland, said employers must ensure
OL,20,Fthe safety and dignity of staff at
OL,21,FChristmas parties.
