OL,6,F"We are currently in the middle of the
OL,7,FChristmas party season. We know that
OL,8,Fstaff parties and outings are
OL,9,Fimportant for team building and for
OL,10,Frecognition and reward, but employers
OL,11,Fmust ensure that everyone attending is
OL,12,Fsafe and that their dignity is
OL,13,Frespected," she said.
OL,15,F"Employers must ensure that all staff
OL,16,Fare fully aware of the standard of
OL,17,Fbehaviour that is expected of them.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@KO]wD@AOU
