OL,6,F"Employees should also be aware of the
OL,7,Fconsequences of their actions should
OL,8,Fthey behave inappropriately at a staff
OL,9,FChristmas party or outing as these are
OL,10,Fan extension of the workplace."
OL,12,FIn a statement, the Equality
OL,13,FCommission for Northern Ireland said:
OL,14,F"In settling its case, the Northern
OL,15,FIreland Human Rights Commission has
OL,16,Facknowledged that Ms Hermosilla is a
OL,17,Fvalued employee and further
OL,18,Facknowledges the significant upset and
OL,19,Fdistress she felt as a result of being
OL,20,Fsubject to harassment by a colleague.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@_O]vD@AOU
