OL,6,F"Furthermore, it has affirmed its
OL,7,Fstrong commitment to the principle of
OL,8,Fequality of opportunity in employment
OL,9,Fand will liaise with ECNI to review
OL,10,Fits equal opportunities and dignity at
OL,11,Fwork policies.
OL,13,F"The colleague has apologised for any
OL,14,Fupset caused. As part of the
OL,15,Fsettlement terms, Ms Hermosilla and
OL,16,Fthe colleague have agreed to put the
OL,17,Fmatters behind them and to work
OL,18,Ftogether going forward on an ongoing
OL,19,Fbasis including in face-to-face
OL,20,Fsettings as necessary. They agreed
OL,21,Fthat mediation was not appropriate."
